==================
install CocoaPods:
-----------------

$ [sudo] gem install cocoapods
$ pod setup
$ cd /path/to/MyProject
$ touch Podfile
$ edit Podfile
//config your Podfile
//************************************************

source 'https://github.com/CocoaPods/Specs.git'
platform :ios, '8.1'

//************************************************

//then run the following command 
$ pod install


